104
00:09:10,522 --> 00:09:11,300
This is you.

105
00:09:11,914 --> 00:09:12,481
This is not me.

106
00:09:12,487 --> 00:09:12,977
This is you.

107
00:09:13,842 --> 00:09:18,454
Klaudia, I remember having a completely different outfit at that time. 

