163
00:13:26,950 --> 00:13:30,534
I called her first because I stole her phone number 
from Grandma's mobile.

164
00:13:30,706 --> 00:13:32,504
And, what did you tell her?

165
00:13:32,723 --> 00:13:36,144
At first it was the answering machine.

166
00:13:36,244 --> 00:13:39,482
Then, I gave Tola her phone number. 

167
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:47,484
Tola SMSed her and Bożena called her back. 

168
00:13:47,680 --> 00:13:53,007
After they talked, Tola was crying.

169
00:13:53,176 --> 00:13:57,490
I was furious because Bożena didn't call me at all. 

170
00:13:57,804 --> 00:14:03,385
I texted her to tell her how bad I felt 
about it and she called me back immediately.

171
00:14:03,591 --> 00:14:04,417
And?

172
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:11,656
She started crying and giving excuses 
for what she did in the past.

173
00:14:11,976 --> 00:14:17,131
