175
00:14:22,393 --> 00:14:26,524
Maybe she'll contact you again when you turn 30?

176
00:14:26,826 --> 00:14:36,806
Aren't you afraid that after you meet her,
she'll disappear from your life again? 

177
00:14:37,257 --> 00:14:40,452
