178
00:14:40,724 --> 00:14:43,021
I know it's risky.

179
00:14:43,225 --> 00:14:50,181
She's been in touch with everyone else but you. 

180
00:14:50,946 --> 00:14:55,238
She could have talked to you just for a second
 to see what you're like. 

181
00:14:55,671 --> 00:15:01,179
She's forgotten about you 
and now you want to hit the fucking road?

182
00:15:01,361 --> 00:15:05,257
Just to see Paris? To see what she's like?

183
00:15:05,892 --> 00:15:08,841
I don't know if I should go or not…

184
00:15:09,165 --> 00:15:15,345
Don't you worry about anything.
Now you're with Dad. I'll help if I can. 

185
00:15:15,533 --> 00:15:25,405
I'll send you money from time to time. 
If you want, you can come here in five or six months. 

186
00:15:25,962 --> 00:15:30,861
Karolina will come first and see what it's like here. Hello?

187
00:15:31,458 --> 00:15:32,819
I'm here.

188
00:15:33,185 --> 00:15:38,971
She can stay with me because I live alone.

189
00:15:39,071 --> 00:15:41,244
I've got a job. 

190
00:15:41,585 --> 00:15:49,838
I haven't told this to Karolina, but I think 
she's going through a hard time now. 

191
00:15:50,369 --> 00:15:52,970
I think she has my character.

192
