That's my impression of her. I've tried to learn from 
my own mistakes and I want her to do the same. 

194
00:16:06,572 --> 00:16:10,981
I don't want you girls to make similar mistakes
like me and your father. 

195
00:16:11,394 --> 00:16:18,367
I'd like you to settle down,
 but Karolina seems to be very much like me.

196
00:16:20,957 --> 00:16:27,603
That's why I'd like her to come here. 
Maybe I could help by telling her about 

197
00:16:27,903 --> 00:16:36,096
the mistakes I've made. 
We haven't seen each other for such a long time. 

198
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:37,544
Right.

199
00:16:37,737 --> 00:16:43,864
We have a chance to change things for better. 
And then, we'll see…

200
00:16:44,299 --> 00:16:49,734
