201
00:16:51,056 --> 00:16:54,468
I'm 160 cm tall and I'm a blonde.

202
00:16:55,683 --> 00:16:58,188
I'm slim and I weigh 48 kg.

203
00:16:58,859 --> 00:17:00,859
