Last time I saw you, you also had long hair.

212
00:17:26,964 --> 00:17:28,359
Who is it?

213
00:17:28,499 --> 00:17:29,131
What?

214
00:17:29,258 --> 00:17:30,734
Who was it?

215
00:17:31,180 --> 00:17:35,057
It's a friend of mine. He drove me home.

216
00:17:35,157 --> 00:17:39,328
I've told him my children are coming over. 

